        file - is a file content
        name - is a name of a part
        fileName - is filename of a part
        calculateContentType - enables calculation of content type. It sets Content-Type to application/octet-stream when calculateContentType is false or it is not possible to get mime. It is possible to change content type to another by invocation of setContentType(String)
